column2: >When it comes to playing video games, having a keyboard that offers good visibility of the keys in the dark is essential. It has a modern and elegant design, as well as customizable LEDs that can be programmed by color and brightness to highlight the desired keys.

Additionally, it has additional features like pre-programmed macros and full RGB control of the internal buttons for better performance during competitive games.
